             deposed to the same effect, and found in the garden, behind the warehouse, thirteen hoops tied up as they are now; no hoops were kept there.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17891209-70-person677">
                  John
                   Allison
               <interp inst="t17891209-70-person677" type="surname" value="Allison"></interp>
